    Algebra.Semigroup<A>
    A Semigroup is an algebraic structure consisting of Some type A An associative binary operation combine, such that combine(combine(x,y),z) == combine(x,combine(y,z)) for any x,y,z of type A. Technically a Semigroup is the same as a java.util.function.BiFunction<A,A,A>.
